ve Ricci\ncurvature implies the quantum Beckner's inequality, from which the transport\ncost and Poincar\\'{e} inequalities can follow.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 13 Jul 2022 18:19:24 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2022 12:51:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-27"}
