ng of the magnetic moments leads to a\nnet ferromagnetic component along b-axis, parallel to the chain direction. The\nordered moments are fully compensated in the ac-plane.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2022 02:28:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-07-15"}
