ual to or less than 2 deg and the flow phenomena of the training data\nare similar to that of the test data. For this reason, training data should be\nprepared at least every 4 deg. Finally, the demonstration of SPPIV as a\nreal-time flow observation was conducted for the first time. In this\ndemonstration, the real-time measurement is found to be possible at a sampling\nrate of 2000 Hz at 20 or less processing points in the top 10 modes estimation\nas expected by the off-line analyses.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 14 Jul 2022 09:33:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Jul 2022 08:00:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 30 Aug 2022 00:32:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-31"}
